snippet.title: Strobophagia Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist the game on STEAM (Free demo available): https://store.steampowered.com/app/1266680/Strobophagia__Rave_Horror/

Developer: Green Tile Digital
Feel free to support our efforts on Pateron
https://www.patreon.com/greentiledigital

Strobophagia is a psychedelic horror game, where you explore the festival grounds of an occult forest rave in an attempt to avoid certain death.

Follow us on social media!

Twitter: https://twitter.com/strobophagia
Discord: https://discord.gg/magPAgz
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/greentiledigital 
Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/strobophagia
